<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Minhas Listas - Meu Carrinho</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/image/logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/pg_mercados.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/listas.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
</head>
<body style="padding-top: 0; background: #f8fafc;">
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="list-container-premium" style="padding-top: 60px;">
        <div class="list-header-premium">
            <div class="list-title-group">
                <h1 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0077ff 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Minhas Listas</h1>
                <p style="color: #64748b;">Organize suas compras e compare a economia total</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/" class="btn-back-premium" style="color: #1e293b; border-color: #e2e8f0;">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Voltar ao Início
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="item-list-premium" style="background: white; border-color: #f1f5f9;">
            <!-- Exemplo de Lista Ativa -->
            <div class="item-premium" style="border-left: 5px solid #0077ff;">
                <div class="item-content">
                    <span class="item-title" style="color: #1e293b;">🛒 Compras do Mês - Abril</span>
                    <div class="item-info">
                        <span class="price-pill">Total: R$ 420,50</span>
                        <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3"></i> Criada em: 29/03/2026</span>
                        <span style="color: #059669;"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i> Economia: R$ 45,20</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item-actions">
                    <a href="#" class="btn-action btn-edit"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Detalhes</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-action btn-delete"><i class="bi bi-trash"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Exemplo de Lista por Mercado -->
            <div class="item-premium" style="border-left: 5px solid #22c55e;">
                <div class="item-content">
                    <span class="item-title" style="color: #1e293b;">🍅 Churrasco de Domingo (Atacadão)</span>
                    <div class="item-info">
                        <span class="price-pill">Total: R$ 185,20</span>
                        <span><i class="bi bi-cart-check"></i> 12 itens selecionados</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item-actions">
                    <a href="#" class="btn-action btn-edit"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> Detalhes</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-action btn-delete"><i class="bi bi-trash"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Seção de Criar Nova Lista -->
            <div style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; padding: 40px; border: 2px dashed #e2e8f0; border-radius: 24px;">
                <i class="bi bi-plus-circle" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #0077ff; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;"></i>
                <h3 style="color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px;">Criar nova lista de compras</h3>
                <p style="color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 20px;">Dê um nome para sua lista e comece a adicionar produtos de diferentes mercados para comparar.</p>
                <form action="/listas/criar" method="POST" style="max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                    <input type="text" name="nome" placeholder="Ex: Mercado da Semana" required 
                           style="flex: 1; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; outline: none;">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-join-premium" style="border: none; cursor: pointer;">Criar</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2024 MeuCarrinho. Sua economia começa aqui.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
